name: Party Animal Kit
description:
The Party Animal kit includes

6 hats (2 of each pattern)  
30 triangle flags (10 of each pattern)
9ft chain (3ft of each pattern)
10 yards of black string


Everything comes flat packed for easy shipping with simple instructions for paper chain and triangle banner assembly. Hats are ready to go right out of the box!

Want everything in just one pattern? 
Want to add solid colors?
Want more of a certain item?
Email or call and we'll create the perfect kit for you!

Each kit is made especially for you so please allow 1-2 weeks for production time.
